lenders.occupational_info:
For the latest in sustainable lighting, Acuity Brands is known worldwide as the best in lighting solutions built for specialized to everyday lighting needs. Our energy efficient lighting technologies offer quality, reliable and sustainable illumination at no extra cost.
 The 4600 Series by Hydrel comes as with an extensive collection of lighting fixtures designed for use in outdoor architectural lighting and as well as landscape lighting purposes. Other applications the 4600 is suitable for are accent lighting and general area lighting for outdoors. The 4600 Series comes equipped with a PAR-20 metal halide and quartz halogen lamp for glare control while the overall body construction is consisted of die-cast aluminum ideal for outdoor wear and tear. 4600 fixtures also feature swivel mounting which gives the 4600 Series flexibility in terms of beam and lighting level control.
 Acuity Brands is the undisputed leader in sustainable lighting solutions; our lighting technologies meet all of your lighting requirements while still maintaining quality, efficient and practical lighting. When it comes to sustainable lighting solutions, Acuity Brands is the world’s leader.
